{"about_the_game":"Build marble runs where your imagination is the only limit.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244540/extras/snapping2.gif?t=1680500491\" /><br>Get started easily with the snap in place system, and turn it off when you want to go beyond the trodden path.<br><br>Use a variety of shapes and materials to bring your creations to life. When they are not enough, use mechanical contraptions to lift, push and steer your marbles. Still can't find the right style or function of a piece? Then you can build your own! Marvelous Marbles is meant to be modded and comes with Steam Workshop integration for easy sharing.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244540/extras/switch.gif?t=1680500491\" /> <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244540/extras/magnetportal.gif?t=1680500491\" /><br><br>Then sit back and relax while watching balls zip through the tracks with the automatic camera system.<br><br>If you have a VR headset, put it on and experience even more immersion. Pick up and place pieces like in real life. But move those expensive vases out of the way, first!<br>Will you dare follow a marble down your creations?<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244540/extras/dish.gif?t=1680500491\" /><br><br>ASMR?<br><br><br>* Over 50 different pieces to build with, across 3 distinct styles.<br><br>* A multitude of balls of various colors and styles.<br><br>* Switches, lifts and other mechanical objects.<br><br>* Moddable.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Defying Gravity","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2244540/74b16ad79df15d62a92d2afc52ebae1e46f2a2e7.jpg"},{"name":"Giant Leap","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/22445